# $Id: EnvVars,v 1.1 2005-08-29 14:56:18 cvsbert Exp $
#
# OpendTect gets its environment variables from:
# * Home_directory/.od/envvars
# * Here ($DTECT_APPL/data/EnvVars)
# * The OS's envioronment
#
# Exception: the variables used to reach Home_directory or the user
#		settings directory are always taken from the OS-env.
#
# Format of this file is simple:
# Environment_variable	Value
# Example:
# DTECT_CBAR_POS	Hor
#
